libs.content:
find_library(vdeplug_library_release
            names
                vdeplug
            hints
                ${pc_vde_library_dirs}
            path_suffixes
                x86
    )

find_library(pcre_library_debug
    names
        pcred
        libpcred
    hints
        env pcre_dir
    path_suffixes
        ${lib_path_suffixes}
    paths
        ${pcre_path}
)

find_library(pcre2_library_release
        names
            pcre2-8
            pcre2-8-static
        hints
            env pcre_dir
        path_suffixes
            x86
        paths
            ${pcre_path}
        )

find_library(pcre2_library_debug
        names
            pcre2-8d
            pcre2-8-staticd
        hints
            env pcre_dir
        path_suffixes
            x86
        paths
            ${pcre_path}
        )
